section.div: An infographics generator with 30+ plugins and 200+ options to display stats about your GitHub account and render them as SVG, Markdown, PDF or JSON!
The plugin that powerfully integrates fzf and (Neo)vim. It is also possible to integrate with coc.nvim.
Forget Vim tabs now you can have buffer tabs
